    public interface Graph
    Interface for structures that let you check if Domains, Operations and Parameters are in the given structure.

      • containsOperation

        int containsOperation(Operation operation,
                      Domain domain,
                      int domainIndex)
        Parameters:

        domain - Domain to be found in the graph
        domainIndex - Index of the domain in the graph
